    if not original or not another:
        return False
    
    # Check if the another name is equal to the original name
    if original == another:
        return True
    
    # Split the original name into individual words

    another_words = another.split()
    
    # Check if the another name is a subset of the original name
    if set(another_words).issubset(original_words):
        return True
    
    # Check if the another name is a subset of the original name in reverse order
    if set(another_words).issubset(original_words[::-1]):
        return True
